import React from 'react' import './list.css' function Uncoiler() { return (

Tech Specifications:

  • High load carrying capacity bearings are incorporated to withstand loads during coiling, reeling and tensioning
  • Custom built up to 2500 KW with increaser/reducer requirement

General:

  • Slitting Line Machine For HR CR COILS AND SHEETS FROM 5-35 TON COIL CAPACITY 0.2-12MM THICKNESS, AND UP TO 2000MM WIDTH.
  • CUT To Length line for HR CR Coils and Sheets From 3-35 Ton coil capacity and up to 6mm wall thickness and up to 2000mm width.
  • Hydraulic Recoiler From 3 to 35 ton Coil capacity Motorized and nonmotorized, Cone Type, Hydraulic Expand Mandrel Type, Double Arm Single Arm.
  • Recoiler For Slitting line
  • Straightener and feeder for CTL and slitting line.
  • NC Servo Feeder SHearing Machine and decompilers
  • ERW tube mill machine
) } export default Uncoiler
